                      <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Respect the community</h4>
                      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Ask permission before taking photos of people and be mindful of local customs</p>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-0.5">2</div>
                    <div>
                      <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Dress appropriately</h4>
                      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Wear comfortable walking shoes, a hat, and bring water and sunscreen</p>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-0.5">3</div>
                    <div>
                      <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">No smoking or littering</h4>
                      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Help us keep the environment clean and healthy for residents</p>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-0.5">4</div>
                    <div>
                      <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Be patient and respectful</h4>
                      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Remember that Dzaleka is home to many families and communities</p>
